<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="8700000t" end="31200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">音无澄女士并非自杀</p>
<p begin="49600000t" end="79600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">那么我们就来指出真正的犯人吧</p>
<p begin="79600000t" end="95500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">真正的犯人?</p>
<p begin="150500000t" end="170500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">终于走到这个阶段了</p>
<p begin="308200000t" end="331500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">在四季中转瞬即逝之冬</p>
<p begin="331500000t" end="359900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">有位如雪般的美人</p>
<p begin="359900000t" end="382400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">折羽织缎只为祈愿</p>
<p begin="382400000t" end="410800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">落下泪珠化身为鹤</p>
<p begin="410800000t" end="433300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">踏上寻找世界尽头旅途</p>
<p begin="433300000t" end="461700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">沙漠中的少年</p>
<p begin="461700000t" end="484200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">释放了神灯的精灵</p>
<p begin="484200000t" end="512500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">获得无可取代的财富</p>
<p begin="512500000t" end="564700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">精巧隐瞒的真象 形同幻化</p>
<p begin="564700000t" end="598900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">之中能有什么意义?</p>
<p begin="598900000t" end="638500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">人生! 一切! 皆是! 神秘!</p>
<p begin="653900000t" end="698100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">让我们背对太阳</p>
<p begin="698100000t" end="752000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">轻轻为无形的未来染上色彩</p>
<p begin="752000000t" end="800300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">来杯刚泡好热腾腾的红茶吧</p>
<p begin="800300000t" end="829100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">宴会已经开始了</p>
<p begin="829100000t" end="863300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">快告诉我 夜色中的故事</p>
<p begin="890000000t" end="925000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">我已经确认你和音无董事长的交易是事实</p>
<p begin="925000000t" end="945500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">但是还存在一个疑问</p>
<p begin="955100000t" end="966300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">吹雪</p>
<p begin="966300000t" end="992600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">你在杀音无澄的时候</p>
<p begin="992600000t" end="1023900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">为什么不假装成意外或病死呢</p>
<p begin="1023900000t" end="1051800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">你既有妖力又能变换外貌</p>
<p begin="1051800000t" end="1068500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">这点程度应该做得到吧</p>
<p begin="1078900000t" end="1107300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">可见你根本没有杀死音无澄</p>
<p begin="1107300000t" end="1127700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">只是假装成自己下的手</p>
<p begin="1127700000t" end="1164400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">跑去找刚一索取交易的代价吧</p>
<p begin="1192000000t" end="1208700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">您可真是独具慧眼啊</p>
<p begin="1219900000t" end="1232800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">公主殿下</p>
<p begin="1261600000t" end="1292890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">我的确没有杀死那个女人</p>
<p begin="1299190000t" end="1345500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">然而我从头到尾都无意</p>
<p begin="1345500000t" end="1360900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">我在那晚</p>
<p begin="1360900000t" end="1379700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">为了去杀死那个叫澄的女人</p>
<p begin="1379700000t" end="1400900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">变成一只野狗</p>
<p begin="1400900000t" end="1431800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">尽管我从交易后便一直寻找下手的机会</p>
<p begin="1431800000t" end="1456000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">直到那时才终于等到她落单</p>
<p begin="1474300000t" end="1484300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">万一错过这个机会</p>
<p begin="1484300000t" end="1499400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">不知道要等到什么时候</p>
<p begin="1499400000t" end="1520600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">得确实解决她才行</p>
<p begin="1520600000t" end="1560700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">我本来的计画是变成野狗追杀那女人</p>
<p begin="1560700000t" end="1598600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">在很多目击者的地方咬断她喉咙</p>
<p begin="1598600000t" end="1639100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">或是把她逼到马路上, 让她被车撞</p>
<p begin="1647000000t" end="1667900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">结果我万万没想到</p>
<p begin="1667900000t" end="1689100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">那女人竟然在我眼前</p>
<p begin="1689100000t" end="1719200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">被一个埋伏的人类刺杀了</p>
<p begin="1728800000t" end="1750000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">犯人确认那女人断气后</p>
<p begin="1750000000t" end="1770000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">便把包包和钱包乱丢在地上</p>
<p begin="1770000000t" end="1802600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">把钱拿走, 迅速逃离现场了</p>
<p begin="1811800000t" end="1837200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">怎么会做出这种事</p>
<p begin="1837200000t" end="1875600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">这下我和那男人的交易就要泡汤了</p>
<p begin="1875600000t" end="1890600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">这样下去的话…</p>
<p begin="1926900000t" end="1938600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">抢劫啊</p>
<p begin="1938600000t" end="1955600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">谁来抓住那个男人</p>
<p begin="1955600000t" end="1983600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">抓住那个穿黑色外套的男人</p>
<p begin="1983600000t" end="1995300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">他往车站跑了</p>
<p begin="2045300000t" end="2058700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">有人倒在地上</p>
<p begin="2058700000t" end="2075300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">快叫救护车</p>
<p begin="2075300000t" end="2098300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">原来那声惨叫不是被害者喊的</p>
<p begin="2098300000t" end="2115000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">而是你搞的鬼啊</p>
<p begin="2115000000t" end="2125000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">是的</p>
<p begin="2125000000t" end="2160900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">那女人胸口被刺时就已经快断气了</p>
<p begin="2160900000t" end="2195900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">没想到现场伪装竟然是妖狐做的</p>
<p begin="2195900000t" end="2225900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">看来构思符合逻辑的伪证时得费点功夫了</p>
<p begin="2225900000t" end="2248400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">现场没有线索或证据</p>
<p begin="2248400000t" end="2267600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">犯人也不可能出面招认</p>
<p begin="2267600000t" end="2286800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">尽管不是我下的手</p>
<p begin="2286800000t" end="2308100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">但目标的确已经死亡</p>
<p begin="2308100000t" end="2346000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">我认为告诉那男人是我下的手也没关系</p>
<p begin="2346000000t" end="2376500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">便去要求他遵守约定</p>
<p begin="2376500000t" end="2422400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">毕竟我有努力不让他的家人遭受怀疑</p>
<p begin="2422400000t" end="2448600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">所以这算不上是欺骗</p>
<p begin="2448600000t" end="2472800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">也就是说你目击了犯人的长相</p>
<p begin="2472800000t" end="2492400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">也知道那个人是谁</p>
<p begin="2492400000t" end="2516600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">所以为了包庇犯人</p>
<p begin="2516600000t" end="2532500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">才会假扮成被害者</p>
<p begin="2532500000t" end="2559600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">让周遭的人听到那声喊叫</p>
<p begin="2570400000t" end="2592500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">这样啊, 那样的话…</p>
<p begin="2592500000t" end="2618390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">是的, 我做过事前调查</p>
<p begin="2618390000t" end="2640100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">认得出犯人是谁</p>
<p begin="2640100000t" end="2684300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">所以才会大喊让周遭认为犯人是"男人"</p>
<p begin="2694700000t" end="2722700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">这么一来犯人就只有一个人选</p>
<p begin="2730200000t" end="2744800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">那么, 犯人就是…</p>
<p begin="2752300000t" end="2797700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">那男人的长女, 名为薰子的女人</p>
<p begin="2807300000t" end="2830300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">真凶是薰子小姐</p>
<p begin="2852800000t" end="2884100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">薰子小姐当初被认为不可能犯案</p>
<p begin="2884100000t" end="2900300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">但就如我昨天所解释的</p>
<p begin="2900300000t" end="2935800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">只要做点手脚让人误认骨折的时间就可行</p>
<p begin="2935800000t" end="2982500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">她便是用了此手法杀害澄女士</p>
<p begin="2988300000t" end="3015900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">我想跟你谈谈我跟耕也的事</p>
<p begin="3015900000t" end="3029200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">毕竟若不挑这时候</p>
<p begin="3029200000t" end="3048000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">我们根本没办法单独说话</p>
<p begin="3048000000t" end="3096400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">薰子小姐应是埋伏在</p>
<p begin="3096400000t" end="3111800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">借此靠近她</p>
<p begin="3111800000t" end="3142300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">澄女士听到她说不在这里等待</p>
<p begin="3142300000t" end="3168100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">便无法与自己聊私密的事情</p>
<p begin="3168100000t" end="3190200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">应该就没有怀疑, 让她接近了</p>
<p begin="3271600000t" end="3301200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">薰子小姐为了假装成抢劫杀人</p>
<p begin="3301200000t" end="3319900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">从她的包包拿出钱包</p>
<p begin="3319900000t" end="3339500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">只抽出纸币后就逃跑了</p>
<p begin="3351200000t" end="3380400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">薰子姑姑杀了祖母…?</p>
<p begin="3385400000t" end="3394600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">耕也先生</p>
<p begin="3401300000t" end="3428400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">你应该也知道是薰子小姐犯的案吧</p>
<p begin="3435500000t" end="3461700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">被我看穿骨折的诡计时</p>
<p begin="3461700000t" end="3476300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">你并没有矢口否认</p>
<p begin="3476300000t" end="3499300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">反而承认如此计划过</p>
<p begin="3499300000t" end="3534300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">但是谎称最后失败了真是高招</p>
<p begin="3548100000t" end="3574300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">就两位的立场而言</p>
<p begin="3574300000t" end="3598100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">音无董事长这次的企图</p>
<p begin="3598100000t" end="3621100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">肯定让你们感到恐惧不已</p>
<p begin="3621100000t" end="3663600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">尽管董事长只是想让大家得知自己的罪行</p>
<p begin="3663600000t" end="3729900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">对两位来说却像是时隔23年的私人制裁</p>
<p begin="3729900000t" end="3751200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">想必董事长的每一句话</p>
<p begin="3751200000t" end="3770000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">你们听起来都有那种感觉</p>
<p begin="3770000000t" end="3822500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">然而董事长也可能是</p>
<p begin="3822500000t" end="3860000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">所以耕也先生一直保持着观望的态度</p>
<p begin="3860000000t" end="3898800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">结果晋先生竟暴露和亮马先生策划的谋杀</p>
<p begin="3898800000t" end="3919300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">导致事情变得很诡异</p>
<p begin="3925500000t" end="3962600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">于是当你察觉我也有在怀疑你们时</p>
<p begin="3962600000t" end="3983500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">便故意承认了</p>
<p begin="3989800000t" end="4026100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">就算董事长握有你们计划谋杀的证据</p>
<p begin="4026100000t" end="4051100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">也能辩称只是未遂</p>
<p begin="4051100000t" end="4115700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">而你也能借此试探董事长掌握了多少真相</p>
<p begin="4115700000t" end="4162000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">接着莉音小姐提出了</p>
<p begin="4162000000t" end="4210400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">到这里, 耕也先生你应该是</p>
<p begin="4210400000t" end="4270000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">只是在获得结果之前, 你们就先动了手</p>
<p begin="4270000000t" end="4301300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">因为三方碰巧同时进行计画</p>
<p begin="4301300000t" end="4330900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">才会导致如此奇怪的状况</p>
<p begin="4330900000t" end="4376800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">董事长也因此以为自己的计画成功了</p>
<p begin="4376800000t" end="4395600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">因此你判断这次的课题</p>
<p begin="4395600000t" end="4443600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">确实是董事长本人想要赎罪</p>
<p begin="4443600000t" end="4480700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">两位昨晚心情应该平静了不少吧</p>
<p begin="4488200000t" end="4500700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">然后到了今天</p>
<p begin="4500700000t" end="4526100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">音无董事长承认自己的计画</p>
<p begin="4526100000t" end="4568700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">耕也先生则打算就这样让董事长背负罪行</p>
<p begin="4568700000t" end="4591600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">你若是打断董事长</p>
<p begin="4591600000t" end="4618300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">承认薰子小姐的罪行</p>
<p begin="4618300000t" end="4650000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">我也就没必要开口说这些了</p>
<p begin="4659200000t" end="4680900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">正如音无董事长刚才所说</p>
<p begin="4680900000t" end="4717200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">一旦杀人就必须遭受相对的报应</p>
<p begin="4717200000t" end="4745500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">就算杀人让一切圆满顺利</p>
<p begin="4745500000t" end="4768500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">还是逃不过报应的</p>
<p begin="4768500000t" end="4804300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">既然你听完那句话仍旧选择保持沉默</p>
<p begin="4804300000t" end="4832700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">那就只好由我来讲出真相了</p>
<p begin="4832700000t" end="4867700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">这都是为了贯彻音无董事长的信念</p>
<p begin="4894400000t" end="4928200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">岩永小姐, 这又是哪出闹剧?</p>
<p begin="4928200000t" end="4975300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">昨天不就是你否定薰子是犯人的可能性吗</p>
<p begin="4975300000t" end="5006200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">澄女士在最后大喊犯人是男的</p>
<p begin="5006200000t" end="5040800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">也已证实这并非是真凶所做的伪装</p>
<p begin="5040800000t" end="5068300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">那么薰子是最不可能成为犯人的人选吧</p>
<p begin="5068300000t" end="5087900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">薰子小姐和耕也先生你们</p>
<p begin="5087900000t" end="5115100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">后来得知现场有听到被害者喊叫时</p>
<p begin="5115100000t" end="5129700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">应该很惊讶吧</p>
<p begin="5129700000t" end="5159700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">也惊讶这件事竟然对你们有利</p>
<p begin="5159700000t" end="5184290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">这是不是董事长在暗中指使</p>
<p begin="5184290000t" end="5215200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">让警方掌握虚假的情报</p>
<p begin="5215200000t" end="5240590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">你们可能甚至还这样怀疑过</p>
<p begin="5240590000t" end="5265200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">所以对于这次聚会</p>
<p begin="5265200000t" end="5307300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">才更害怕董事长是不是知道自己是凶手了</p>
<p begin="5315700000t" end="5350700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">然而那的确是澄女士喊出来的话语</p>
<p begin="5362400000t" end="5382800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">澄女士为了包庇女儿</p>
<p begin="5382800000t" end="5436600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">挤出最后一丝力气</p>
<p begin="5436600000t" end="5455800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">正因为是亲生女儿</p>
<p begin="5455800000t" end="5481200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">才想保护她不受警方怀疑</p>
<p begin="5493400000t" end="5523000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">这你昨天也否定了吧</p>
<p begin="5523000000t" end="5538400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">你说如果是谋杀的话</p>
<p begin="5538400000t" end="5564200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">犯人动手时会避免引人注目</p>
<p begin="5564200000t" end="5582600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">堵住被害者的嘴</p>
<p begin="5582600000t" end="5603900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">并且为了不留下线索</p>
<p begin="5603900000t" end="5628100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">在确认对方死亡后才离开现场</p>
<p begin="5628100000t" end="5642300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">耕也</p>
<p begin="5642300000t" end="5672300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">如果是熟人计划好的犯案</p>
<p begin="5672300000t" end="5692300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">被害者根本没机会喊叫</p>
<p begin="5692300000t" end="5744000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">所以才得出是陌生人冲动犯案的结论</p>
<p begin="5744000000t" end="5762000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">毕竟是第一次杀人</p>
<p begin="5762000000t" end="5797800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">所以薰子小姐没能</p>
<p begin="5797800000t" end="5832400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">看见对方倒地不动就觉得没问题了</p>
<p begin="5832400000t" end="5870000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">然而澄女士还是挤出了最后一丝力气</p>
<p begin="5870000000t" end="5899600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">为女儿着想的母爱真是伟大呢</p>
<p begin="5899600000t" end="5920900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">少在那边胡言乱语</p>
<p begin="5976700000t" end="6003900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">薰子小姐有测量对方的脉搏吗</p>
<p begin="6013000000t" end="6033900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">有确认呼吸吗</p>
<p begin="6033900000t" end="6052200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">为了不在刀上留下指纹</p>
<p begin="6052200000t" end="6071800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">应该戴着手套吧</p>
<p begin="6071800000t" end="6101000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">那样真的能好好确认生命迹象吗</p>
<p begin="6109000000t" end="6133600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">她从一开始就是为了这个目的</p>
<p begin="6133600000t" end="6160300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">之所以引导我找出虚假的解答</p>
<p begin="6160300000t" end="6184500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">也是为了把耕也姑丈逼入绝境</p>
<p begin="6184500000t" end="6199000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">怎么样啊</p>
<p begin="6199000000t" end="6238300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">薰子说她确认过对方确实断气了</p>
<p begin="6258700000t" end="6282500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">也有证词表示邻近居民赶到时</p>
<p begin="6282500000t" end="6310400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">遗体仍留有余温呢</p>
<p begin="6310400000t" end="6334200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">才死后几分钟的话当然有余温啊</p>
<p begin="6334200000t" end="6360000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">人就算死掉也不会马上变得冰冷</p>
<p begin="6360000000t" end="6395100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">但是有许多人听见死者的呼喊</p>
<p begin="6395100000t" end="6418900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">所以澄女士当时还活着</p>
<p begin="6436400000t" end="6466000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">事到如今已无法确认</p>
<p begin="6466000000t" end="6534000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">还是为了保护集团形象才包庇女儿的罪行</p>
<p begin="6546900000t" end="6569400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">那么, 看来聪明如耕也先生…</p>
<p begin="6569400000t" end="6592000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">面对我从昨天起的各种暗示, 指责</p>
<p begin="6592000000t" end="6607800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">和重重意外发展之后</p>
<p begin="6607800000t" end="6629500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">精神也难以承受了呢</p>
<p begin="6629500000t" end="6643300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">也因此说溜嘴了</p>
<p begin="6654100000t" end="6697100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">毕竟是23年前的事, 没有任何证据</p>
<p begin="6697100000t" end="6728300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">不引出只有犯人才知道的资讯</p>
<p begin="6728300000t" end="6745400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">说再多都只是空谈</p>
<p begin="6745400000t" end="6770000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">耕也先生你刚刚是这么说的</p>
<p begin="6770000000t" end="6813400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">薰子说她确认过对方确实断气了</p>
<p begin="6868100000t" end="6880600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">音无董事长</p>
<p begin="6880600000t" end="6903100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">如您所见, 事件的真凶是薰子小姐</p>
<p begin="6903100000t" end="6920600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">耕也先生则是共犯</p>
<p begin="6925600000t" end="6952700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">不过两人若在计画阶段就已是共犯</p>
<p begin="6952700000t" end="6973200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">以耕也先生的个性</p>
<p begin="6973200000t" end="7008200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">想必不会让身为女性的薰子小姐动手</p>
<p begin="7015300000t" end="7061200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">所以当时应该是薰子小姐独自策划并执行</p>
<p begin="7061200000t" end="7091600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">耕也先生则是在事后才得知的</p>
<p begin="7098700000t" end="7131600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">薰子小姐或许是害怕您这次的课题</p>
<p begin="7131600000t" end="7178400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">时隔23年第一次对耕也先生自白</p>
<p begin="7178400000t" end="7209700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">耕也先生也才因此拼命想包庇她</p>
<p begin="7218000000t" end="7237200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">事件早已过了追诉期</p>
<p begin="7237200000t" end="7273000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">只剩下家人间以及董事长您信念的问题</p>
<p begin="7273000000t" end="7291800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">请各位自行处置吧</p>
<p begin="7291800000t" end="7313100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">就像我一开始所说的</p>
<p begin="7313100000t" end="7352700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">我离开旅馆之后便会把一切全部忘记</p>
<p begin="7359800000t" end="7420300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">我只是想让您明白</p>
<p begin="7431500000t" end="7458700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">您做了有违秩序的事情</p>
<p begin="7458700000t" end="7500800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">因此衍生出必须面对这种真相的因果</p>
<p begin="7500800000t" end="7531200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">如果您当时决心自己动手</p>
<p begin="7531200000t" end="7564200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">或是拒绝了超自然的诱惑</p>
<p begin="7564200000t" end="7584600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">就算实际的凶手是您长女</p>
<p begin="7584600000t" end="7612500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">应该也能相信妻子只是遇上强盗杀人</p>
<p begin="7612500000t" end="7632600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">安享天年才是</p>
<p begin="7652200000t" end="7663400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">九郎学长</p>
<p begin="7663400000t" end="7683900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">我们局外人就此告辞吧</p>
<p begin="7773100000t" end="7782700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">等等</p>
<p begin="7804400000t" end="7834000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">你以为能想走就走吗</p>
<p begin="7906200000t" end="7950000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">(沉睡谋杀)</p>
<p begin="7994600000t" end="8018400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">耕也, 别冲动</p>
<p begin="8018400000t" end="8041300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">这件事就算被警方知道也没什么影响</p>
<p begin="8041300000t" end="8058000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">我们既没资格责备你们</p>
<p begin="8058000000t" end="8075500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">也不打算泄漏出去</p>
<p begin="8075500000t" end="8087200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">我知道</p>
<p begin="8087200000t" end="8120100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">我信任晋先生, 董事长和莉音</p>
<p begin="8120100000t" end="8139700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">因为你们都是音无家的人</p>
<p begin="8139700000t" end="8167700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">但是这两个人不一样吧</p>
<p begin="8167700000t" end="8210700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">首先他们根本没有必要揭露真相</p>
<p begin="8210700000t" end="8233200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">既然如此还特地这么做</p>
<p begin="8233200000t" end="8256900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">肯定是别有用心</p>
<p begin="8256900000t" end="8284500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">不, 这两个人从一开始就很诡异</p>
<p begin="8290300000t" end="8305300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">就算事件已过追诉期</p>
<p begin="8305300000t" end="8339100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">- 传出去仍无法避免舆论</p>
<p begin="8339100000t" end="8347500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">这两个人…</p>
<p begin="8347500000t" end="8377900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">尤其是我无法信任岩永琴子会做出什么事</p>
<p begin="8377900000t" end="8406300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">不能放他们离开这里</p>
<p begin="8406300000t" end="8425900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">我什么都不会做喔</p>
<p begin="8425900000t" end="8468800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">耕也先生这么珍惜薰子小姐</p>
<p begin="8468800000t" end="8514300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">薰子小姐也不惜为了你们的未来动手杀人</p>
<p begin="8514300000t" end="8538900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">要是妨碍这么美好的一对男女</p>
<p begin="8538900000t" end="8572700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">感觉会遭到恋爱之神的天谴呢</p>
<p begin="8572700000t" end="8610200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">我可不想因此弄坏跟学长的关系</p>
<p begin="8610200000t" end="8653200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">所以我不打算继续跟这件事有所牵连</p>
<p begin="8662800000t" end="8702800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">不要鬼扯惹恼人家啦</p>
<p begin="8702800000t" end="8715300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">哪有鬼扯</p>
<p begin="8715300000t" end="8748700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">我只是说出于个人因素不希望有所牵连啊</p>
<p begin="8748700000t" end="8760800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">不好意思</p>
<p begin="8760800000t" end="8780400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">虽然岩永很没礼貌</p>
<p begin="8780400000t" end="8804600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">但我们真的没打算做任何事</p>
<p begin="8804600000t" end="8828400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">不准动, 我可不是在唬人</p>
<p begin="8828400000t" end="8847900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">我承认你很有胆量</p>
<p begin="8847900000t" end="8878000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">但那个大小姐有让你赌命的价值吗</p>
<p begin="8878000000t" end="8919300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">很不巧, 我没有能拿来当赌注的命</p>
<p begin="9111100000t" end="9135300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">这么一来我就不能回头了</p>
<p begin="9135300000t" end="9157000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">你和他都是错误的</p>
<p begin="9157000000t" end="9178300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">我是正确的</p>
<p begin="9178300000t" end="9200400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">而你也还有机会回头</p>
<p begin="9308000000t" end="9340500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">我说过我没有能拿来当赌注的命了</p>
<p begin="9340500000t" end="9353900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">为什么</p>
<p begin="9353900000t" end="9374300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">为什么你还活着</p>
<p begin="9374300000t" end="9392200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">我明明就射中头了</p>
<p begin="9392200000t" end="9421000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">贯穿的子弹还打进墙里了啊</p>
<p begin="9421000000t" end="9448600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">就是…像那个…</p>
<p begin="9448600000t" end="9468600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">时代剧还满常演的吧</p>
<p begin="9468600000t" end="9485700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">叫做刀背砍的情况</p>
<p begin="9485700000t" end="9511100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">子弹哪来的刀背!</p>
<p begin="9511100000t" end="9545700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">在这里发生的事就像一场白日梦</p>
<p begin="9545700000t" end="9579100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">请把我们当作梦里的居民吧</p>
<p begin="9579100000t" end="9607500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">所以我们不受现世的法律和规矩束缚</p>
<p begin="9607500000t" end="9620000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">也没有兴趣</p>
<p begin="9626600000t" end="9639200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">那么各位</p>
<p begin="9639200000t" end="9658800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">这次真的要告辞了</p>
<p begin="9658800000t" end="9688800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">我无意与音无集团敌对</p>
<p begin="9695500000t" end="9732200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">也谢谢音无董事长这次的指教</p>
<p begin="9859800000t" end="9885200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">那之后过了两个星期</p>
<p begin="9885200000t" end="9924000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">23年前的真相被揭露的隔天</p>
<p begin="9924000000t" end="9949900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">薰子姑姑自杀未遂</p>
<p begin="9957800000t" end="9999900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">多亏耕也姑丈及时发现才救回一命</p>
<p begin="9999900000t" end="10021600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">目前仍住院疗养中</p>
<p begin="10027500000t" end="10052900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">据说姑姑因为祖父提出的课题</p>
<p begin="10052900000t" end="10085000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">担心自已的罪行被发现</p>
<p begin="10085000000t" end="10121700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">近一个月来精神状况一直相当不稳定</p>
<p begin="10128800000t" end="10155900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">得知亲戚们已经知道此事的事实</p>
<p begin="10155900000t" end="10175100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">最终让她无法承受</p>
<p begin="10175100000t" end="10211800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">她应该也是一直背负着弑母的罪恶感吧</p>
<p begin="10217600000t" end="10236400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">有片阴影一直存在着</p>
<p begin="10236400000t" end="10260600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">在23年前发生的事件中</p>
<p begin="10260600000t" end="10285200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">杀人的事实与犯人都确实存在</p>
<p begin="10285200000t" end="10304800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">只是一直沉睡着</p>
<p begin="10311500000t" end="10336090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">要是她能隐瞒真相</p>
<p begin="10336090000t" end="10354000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">就能避免这样的结果</p>
<p begin="10359900000t" end="10387000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">即便如此她还是揭露了真相</p>
<p begin="10387000000t" end="10413690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">我感觉这当中存在着某种未知的…</p>
<p begin="10413690000t" end="10454100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">对岩永琴子来说是信念或规则的东西</p>
<p begin="10454100000t" end="10478290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">她对妨碍者绝不留情</p>
<p begin="10492100000t" end="10503800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">真是太冷酷了</p>
<p begin="10554700000t" end="10566800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">叔叔</p>
<p begin="10566800000t" end="10587200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">打扰了</p>
<p begin="10587200000t" end="10610100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">他去探病回程顺道过来的样子</p>
<p begin="10615100000t" end="10626400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">欢迎光临</p>
<p begin="10632600000t" end="10667700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">唯一值得庆幸的</p>
<p begin="10675600000t" end="10719000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">薰子姐姐有耕也细心照料</p>
<p begin="10719000000t" end="10738600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">爸爸的病情则恶化得很快</p>
<p begin="10738600000t" end="10774900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">大概是原本的肿瘤加上精神劳累造成的吧</p>
<p begin="10774900000t" end="10787400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">这样啊</p>
<p begin="10794500000t" end="10822400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">祖父在那之后也倒下住院了</p>
<p begin="10829500000t" end="10850800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">他本来想制裁自己的罪孽</p>
<p begin="10850800000t" end="10880000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">却反而揭露了薰子姑姑的罪行</p>
<p begin="10880000000t" end="10904200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">还得面对该不该照自己当初声明的信念</p>
<p begin="10904200000t" end="10941700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">对薰子姑姑做出制裁</p>
<p begin="10941700000t" end="10958400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">而这一切的起因</p>
<p begin="10958400000t" end="10993800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">也可以说是把那个大小姐找来的祖父本人</p>
<p begin="10993800000t" end="11027600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">自责的心情大概会加快消耗他的寿命吧</p>
<p begin="11027600000t" end="11062300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">岩永琴子的那些说明确定没错吗</p>
<p begin="11062300000t" end="11071800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">是啊</p>
<p begin="11071800000t" end="11101000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">薰子姐姐当时为了和耕也结婚</p>
<p begin="11101000000t" end="11125200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">以及保护他的事业</p>
<p begin="11125200000t" end="11154400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">暗自决定谋杀妈妈</p>
<p begin="11154400000t" end="11190300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">她自己执行了令人误认骨折时间的伪装</p>
<p begin="11190300000t" end="11222000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">直到最近也一直瞒着耕也</p>
<p begin="11222000000t" end="11249500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">爸爸提出课题使得这段过去又浮上台面</p>
<p begin="11249500000t" end="11268700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">她才不得已向耕也求助</p>
<p begin="11268700000t" end="11291200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">耕也也答应要帮助她</p>
<p begin="11301200000t" end="11330400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">实在不该跟那个大小姐扯上关系的</p>
<p begin="11330400000t" end="11350900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">她的真面目太深不可测了</p>
<p begin="11350900000t" end="11381300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">是啊, 我也不想再跟她扯上关系</p>
<p begin="11392200000t" end="11427600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">那个叫樱川九郎的人也是</p>
<p begin="11440100000t" end="11474700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">他们两个真的是人类吗</p>
<p begin="11485200000t" end="11523100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">我不是找你们来听我抱怨的</p>
<p begin="11523100000t" end="11551500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">那个结果是我自己招来的</p>
<p begin="11551500000t" end="11586500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">也并没有偏离我的信念</p>
<p begin="11586500000t" end="11631100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">尽管你并没有看在情面上葬送事件的真相</p>
<p begin="11631100000t" end="11661200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">因此怨恨你们也太不合理了</p>
<p begin="11661200000t" end="11681200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">要抱怨的话我也会听啦</p>
<p begin="11681200000t" end="11705800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">我可没有那么无情</p>
<p begin="11705800000t" end="11744200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">我想你对之后的事应该没有兴趣</p>
<p begin="11744200000t" end="11778400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">这样把你们叫来也算是违反约定了吧</p>
<p begin="11778400000t" end="11819700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">但我有件事想确认一下</p>
<p begin="11819700000t" end="11847600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">你是叫樱川九郎对吧</p>
<p begin="11847600000t" end="11887200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">我听说你是樱川六花小姐的堂弟</p>
<p begin="11909300000t" end="11932300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">您知道六花姐吗</p>
<p begin="11932300000t" end="12000300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">其实我一开始就是</p>
<p begin="12000300000t" end="12080300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">我听说有间医院长期住着一个</p>
<p begin="12080300000t" end="12098700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">也听说只要找她谘询</p>
<p begin="12098700000t" end="12127900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">事情通常都能迎刃而解</p>
<p begin="12127900000t" end="12172100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">我不知道她长期住院的理由</p>
<p begin="12172100000t" end="12200000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">但我毕竟是曾跟妖狐进行交易的人</p>
<p begin="12200000000t" end="12234700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">对于异于常人的人物总有些兴趣</p>
<p begin="12234700000t" end="12268900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">所以曾要求跟她见过一次面</p>
<p begin="12268900000t" end="12283000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">然后…</p>
<p begin="12283000000t" end="12312300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">我发现她是货真价实的</p>
<p begin="12312300000t" end="12326800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">尽管非常美丽</p>
<p begin="12326800000t" end="12360600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">但她在我眼里明显不是人类</p>
<p begin="12360600000t" end="12402700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">大约2个月前, 我在街上偶然看见她</p>
<p begin="12402700000t" end="12431500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">我正烦恼不知如何处置过去的罪行</p>
<p begin="12431500000t" end="12471100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">感觉遇见她应是上天的安排便前去搭话</p>
<p begin="12471100000t" end="12500800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">因为我认为与怪异牵扯而生的烦恼</p>
<p begin="12500800000t" end="12537100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">找这样怪异的人物商量或许更恰当</p>
<p begin="12537100000t" end="12577500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">她虽然面露困惑, 仍听我说了</p>
<p begin="12577500000t" end="12613800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">我没告诉她关于杀人的部分</p>
<p begin="12613800000t" end="12637200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">只问了我过去曾与怪物交易</p>
<p begin="12637200000t" end="12669300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">有没有什么方法可以赎罪</p>
<p begin="12669300000t" end="12740600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">或是能否用她的力量给我一个应有的未来</p>
<p begin="12740600000t" end="12758100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">结果她…</p>
<p begin="12768100000t" end="12806100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">跟我拥有相同力量的堂弟, 还有…</p>
<p begin="12817300000t" end="12863600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">她告诉我, 你们应该能实现我的愿望</p>
<p begin="12876600000t" end="12896600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">我虽然半信半疑</p>
<p begin="12896600000t" end="12915800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">不过调查了琴子小姐之后</p>
<p begin="12915800000t" end="12942900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">查到许多不得了的情报</p>
<p begin="12943300000t" end="12988800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">实际见面后也感受到不寻常的力量</p>
<p begin="12988800000t" end="13022500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">虽然这么说或许会惹你们不悦</p>
<p begin="13022500000t" end="13067600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">不过在我看来, 你们两个也不太像人类</p>
<p begin="13067600000t" end="13094300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">所以我才选择信任并委托你们帮忙</p>
<p begin="13094300000t" end="13112600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">不过现在想想</p>
<p begin="13112600000t" end="13147700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">为什么我会听从名为六花的女性的建议</p>
<p begin="13147700000t" end="13166400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">选择相信你呢</p>
<p begin="13166400000t" end="13193500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">突然让我觉得很奇怪</p>
<p begin="13193500000t" end="13248200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">难道说我是被她引导到会这样做的未来了</p>
<p begin="13270700000t" end="13288600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">那个人和九郎学长</p>
<p begin="13288600000t" end="13319500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">并不是任何未来都能挑选</p>
<p begin="13319500000t" end="13355400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">终究只能决定可能性比较高的未来</p>
<p begin="13355400000t" end="13382900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">音无董事长您因为过去的经验</p>
<p begin="13382900000t" end="13409200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">有容易相信怪异的倾向</p>
<p begin="13409200000t" end="13457100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">这次也强烈希望透过怪异解决问题</p>
<p begin="13457100000t" end="13473400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">六花小姐能干涉的…</p>
<p begin="13473400000t" end="13509300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">顶多只有消除您对此的犹豫吧</p>
<p begin="13509300000t" end="13543900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">您并没有被她随意操控</p>
<p begin="13543900000t" end="13556400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">这样啊</p>
<p begin="13556400000t" end="13578900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">应该是吧</p>
<p begin="13578900000t" end="13611500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">请问您知道六花小姐现在人在哪吗</p>
<p begin="13611500000t" end="13631100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">我们那次之后就没见过面了</p>
<p begin="13631100000t" end="13651500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">也没有交换联络方式</p>
<p begin="13651500000t" end="13692000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">她应该不在乎结果如何吧</p>
<p begin="13692000000t" end="13714100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">不过她是不是早已预料事情会变这样</p>
<p begin="13714100000t" end="13735300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">才把你们推荐给我呢</p>
<p begin="13735300000t" end="13748300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">我不知道</p>
<p begin="13748300000t" end="13775000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">毕竟那个人对我来说也很棘手</p>
<p begin="13784100000t" end="13820800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">没想到背后竟然有六花小姐牵线</p>
<p begin="13820800000t" end="13867100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">我就觉得董事长来拜托我的发展太顺利</p>
<p begin="13867100000t" end="13890100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">却没料到是这么回事</p>
<p begin="13890100000t" end="13918000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">她为什么要把这件事推给我处理呢</p>
<p begin="13918000000t" end="13933000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">就算是六花小姐</p>
<p begin="13933000000t" end="13948000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">也不可能凭那么一点情报</p>
<p begin="13948000000t" end="13987700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">看穿事件的结果和过程啊</p>
<p begin="13987700000t" end="14014400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">该不会只是想骚扰我吧</p>
<p begin="14014400000t" end="14039800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">我能想到的理由有两个</p>
<p begin="14046100000t" end="14075300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">一个是让你集中注意力在这件事上</p>
<p begin="14075300000t" end="14120700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">无暇察觉她接下来准备做什么</p>
<p begin="14120700000t" end="14147800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">的确比单纯骚扰还有可能</p>
<p begin="14147800000t" end="14209100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">另一个是让我见证</p>
<p begin="14216200000t" end="14232100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">事到如今这样做吗</p>
<p begin="14232100000t" end="14260000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">学长你已经看过很多次了吧</p>
<p begin="14260000000t" end="14278800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">是没错</p>
<p begin="14278800000t" end="14308400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">但这次的事件与人类有密切关联</p>
<p begin="14308400000t" end="14344300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">她可能认为更能凸显你的处事特征</p>
<p begin="14344300000t" end="14384300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">你这次为了维护秩序完全不讲情面</p>
<p begin="14384300000t" end="14408100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">明知会导致悲惨结局</p>
<p begin="14408100000t" end="14428500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">仍揭露了真相</p>
<p begin="14428500000t" end="14461900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">你会为了应该守护的秩序毫不留情</p>
<p begin="14461900000t" end="14491500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">她或许认为这次能让我更加看清这点</p>
<p begin="14491500000t" end="14502800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">不不不</p>
<p begin="14502800000t" end="14532400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">怎么把我讲得像残暴冷酷的机器一样</p>
<p begin="14532400000t" end="14556600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">董事长做了坏事</p>
<p begin="14556600000t" end="14583700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443">纠正错误跟情面有什么关系</p>
<p begin="14584100000t" end="14606600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444">是啊, 你这样就行了</p>
<p begin="14606600000t" end="14622900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445">不需要烦恼</p>
<p begin="14622900000t" end="14645000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446">反正你的脑袋八成没有用来烦恼的神经</p>
<p begin="14645000000t" end="14687900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447">学长你这样讲话才叫冷酷无情吧</p>
<p begin="14767600000t" end="14783900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448">九郎啊…</p>
<p begin="14783900000t" end="14826400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449">你还没察觉到琴子小姐的可怕之处吗</p>
<p begin="14970300000t" end="15000300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450">(待续)</p>
